{"tid":2079002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度餐飲酒店協會宣布不接待中國人 ，小米用「印度製造」標語遮掩招牌","createTime":"2020-06-25T12:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T01:12:33.000Z","uid":48040,"like":558,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd8283e8e2e123ce2e16d40629b1270e17ce2a0","tid":2079002,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"「不再接待中國人」，這一決定涉及7萬5千家酒店，得到了當地餐飲酒店雇主協會這一當地最大行業協會之一的支持，他們拒絕繼續接待中國顧客，協會主席Sandeep Khandelwal表示，會以此來「支持印度政府，尤其是現在和中國已經處於半個戰爭狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社新德里站指出，小米手機本來在印度市場頗受歡迎，在當地還擁有工廠，但<span style=\"color: orange;\">近期已經開始遮掩其店面與標識，用巨大的&ldquo;印度製造&rdquo;標語蓋住</span>。小米孟買店的店主Jignesh表示，&ldquo;公司負責人讓我們這麼做，因為我們要自我保護，避免受到示威者或者是政治人物的潛在衝擊，現在反華情緒很高&rdquo;。但Jignesh也指出，&ldquo;市場對於小米智能手機的需求完全沒有減少，人們繼續買得很歡&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://rfi.my/67PB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frfi.my%2F67PB&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=e055eae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rfi.my/67PB</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nTwitter戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275413556494655496?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275413556494655496%3Fs%3D20&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=0a7d7fa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1275413556494655496%3Fs%3D20&h=eee74964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1275413556494655496?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"6f37af4c24c50e7b55eb66cb1289c81dca1cdf1e","tid":2079002,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c33d6ed02a881a50d915fdc05456a3b919d9344","tid":2079002,"uid":290883,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"支人與狗，"},{"pid":"1efd1650620dba20bc1b326fc478cf009eac3a22","tid":2079002,"uid":343361,"like